rComments: Avoid this teacher at any cost. He is really boring

He was a very good prof, very wary of his students' success. His explanations were always clear and the class was dynamic and interactive. Still, he got frustrated when we didn't remember some of the basic concepts from first year econ. If you go to class and do the readings, you should be able to have a good grade without too much trouble.

Disorganized and poor time management. Bad at explaining concepts clearly/poor communication. Lectures are not useful exam prep, so you have to teach yourself the subject and be motivated. However, he's very nice and tries to improve...
